title: Full Show (Dak got "his power back," Lakers lose in latest preseason game, OBJ free agency latest)
description:
00:00 CeeDee Lamb: Dak has "got his power back. You feel it in every throw."
24:58 Lakers lose 118-113 to Minnesota in latest preseason game
51:11 Sean McVay: OBJ hasn't gotten our final offer yet
1:04:16 Latest on Davante Adams incident in KC
1:17:05 Should we believe that Dak still has his "power back" when it comes to throwing?
1:32:29 Draymond Green returns to the Warriors today after "letting the air clear"
1:42:00 Will running the ball or the play of Cooper Rush be more vital for a DAL win?
1:49:19 Should Josh Allen and the Bills be the favorites in this AFC showdown?
1:53:32 Zion twists left ankle in preseason game, says he is "fine"
